common-blocks.name: Common Blocks Kill You
common-blocks.description: This project is a Minecraft Java plugin that causes you to die if you touch grass, netherrack or end stone.

jump-explode.name: You Jump You Explode
jump-explode.description: This project is a Minecraft Java plugin that causes an explosion underneath you whenever you jump.

lava-rising.name: Lava Rising
lava-rising.description: This project is a customisable Minecraft Java plugin that causes lava to rise by a specified amount whenever you run a command.

water-rising.name: Water Rising
water-rising.description: This project is a customisable Minecraft Java plugin that causes water to rise by a specified amount whenever you run a command and gives players hunger when they are under the water.

animal-capture.name: Animal Capture
animal-capture.description: This project is a Minecraft Java plugin that puts two teams head-to-head in a race to capture as many animals, and gain as many points, as they can.

outcasts-finale.name: Outcasts Finale
outcasts-finale.description: This project is a Minecraft Java plugin that adds new custom items to the game that the Outcasters came up with, each with custom crafting recipies and abilities.

recording-indicator.name: Recording Indicator
recording-indicator.description: This project is a Minecraft Java plugin that adds a simple indicator on the tab list to display if a user is live or recording.

yrrah-birthday.name: Yrrah's Birthday
yrrah-birthday.description: This is a plugin made for Yrrah's birthday where the goal is to craft and deposit as many cakes as possible with ingredients from around the map.

jst-bot.name: JST Discord Bot
jst-bot.description: This is a fully-featured, multipurpose Discord bot with everything from moderation to management.

buffcore.name: BuffCore
buffcore.description: The main plugin utilised by the Buff SMP. It has the core features of the buffs and mythic items with many other additions.

teli-studios.name: Teli Studios
teli-studios.descrtiption: My new indie game studio founded by me and a friend.
